<p>Featuring a nice side panel window and plenty of room for your components (despite its small size), it‚Äôs great for a mid-range build.</p>

<p>Although it doesn‚Äôt have a ton of RGB lights or crazy fans, the 400C is still sure to impress.</p>

<p>It‚Äôs definitely more focused on functionality than looks, but you can deck it out with RGB lighting if you wish.</p>

<p>Corsair is one of my favorite companies, and their cases are probably one of the biggest reasons why that is.</p>

